<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport"
	content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
<title>Form</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/Contact-Form-Clean.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
	<h1 class="text-center">NMTSA Refferal&nbsp;</h1>
	<p class="text-center">
		<br>In order to better understand your therapy and scheduling
		needs, please fill out the following information. Should you have
		further questions, please feel free to contact us at <a
			href="mailto:info@nmtsa.org">info@nmtsa.org</a>. <br> <br>
	</p>
	<div class="text-center">
		<form>
			<div style="margin-right: 49%;">
				<label
					class="text-nowrap text-right text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-center"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><strong>First Name*</strong><br>
					<input class="form-control form-control-sm d-sm-flex" type="text"
					style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"
					placeholder="First name of the person to receive services"><br></label>
				<label
					class="text-nowrap text-right text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-center"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><strong>Last
						Name*&nbsp;</strong><br> <input
					class="form-control form-control-sm d-sm-flex" type="text"
					style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"
					placeholder="Last name of the person to receive services"><br></label><label
					class="text-nowrap text-right text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-center"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><strong>Birthdate*
						&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br> <input
					class="form-control form-control-sm d-sm-flex" type="text"
					style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"
					placeholder="mm/dd/yyyy"><br></label><label
					class="text-nowrap text-center text-md-center text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-center"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><br> <strong>Diagnosis*</strong><small
					class="form-text text-muted"><br>Please check all that
						apply<br> <br></small><br> <br> <strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br>
					<br></label><label
					class="text-center text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-center"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><br> <strong>Primary
						Phone Number*</strong>&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br> <input
					class="form-control form-control-sm" type="tel"
					style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;"></label><label
					class="text-center text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-end"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><br> <strong>Parent/Guardian
						First Name*&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br> <br> <input
					class="form-control form-control-sm d-sm-flex" type="text"
					style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"
					placeholder="mm/dd/yyyy"></label> <label
					class="text-center text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-end"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><br> <strong>Parent/Guardian
						Last Name*&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br> <br> <input
					class="form-control form-control-sm d-sm-flex" type="text"
					style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"
					placeholder="mm/dd/yyyy"></label><label
					class="text-nowrap text-right text-dark d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-sm-start align-items-sm-center"
					style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><br> <strong>Mailing
						Address</strong><br> <br> <strong>* &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br>
					<br> <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="email"
					style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;"></label>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	<script src="assets/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="assets/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>